    <item>
      <title>德国经济陷入衰退，2024 年不再增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/german-economy-in-recession-with-no-more-growth-seen-in-2024</link>
      <description><![CDATA[彭博社的一项调查显示，德国正遭受轻度经济衰退，2024 年全年的产出将持平——凸显了欧洲最大经济体的萎靡不振。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/german-economy-in-recession-with-no-more-growth-seen-in-2024</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 14 Oct 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>调查显示瑞士央行将再降息两次，将利率降至 0.5%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/snb-will-make-two-more-cuts-to-bring-rate-to-0-5-survey-shows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[彭博社调查显示，瑞士央行的宽松周期将延续到明年，经济学家目前预测，在即将召开的12月和3月政策会议上，该行还将再降息两次。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/snb-will-make-two-more-cuts-to-bring-rate-to-0-5-survey-shows</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 14 Oct 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧元区就业市场降温引发要求欧洲央行加快降息的呼声</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/euro-zone-s-cooling-jobs-market-feeds-calls-for-faster-ecb-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[经过多年出人意料的复苏之后，欧元区劳动力市场终于出现裂痕——促使欧洲央行更快地降低利率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/euro-zone-s-cooling-jobs-market-feeds-calls-for-faster-ecb-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 14 Oct 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国股市克服波动，早盘收高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/chinese-stocks-rebound-as-ministry-hints-at-more-fiscal-support</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者评估财政部周末宣布的支持措施的潜在影响，中国股市在早盘震荡中收盘走高。]]></description>
