    <item>
      <title>高盛因最新刺激措施上调中国经济增长预测</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/goldman-sachs-upgrades-china-growth-forecasts-on-latest-stimulus</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在北京方面出台一系列促进经济增长的措施（包括周末宣布的增加公共支出的计划）之后，高盛集团上调了对中国 2024 年和 2025 年经济增长的预测。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/goldman-sachs-upgrades-china-growth-forecasts-on-latest-stimulus</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 14 Oct 2024 01:23:47 GMT</pubDate>
